Day:1 Started learning TypeScript

Completed with introduction and basic environment setup for TypeScript.

TypeScript

>>It is a language for application-scale JavaScript development.
>>TypeScript is a typed superset of JS that compiles to plain JS.

Design Goals

>>Adds support for classes, interfaces and modules.
>>Development tooling support

Installation 
yarn global add typescript

This will install TypeScript globally. After installation, it will be available via the tsc command.